==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tiptop
<hw>Tip"top`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Tip</ets> end +
<ets>top</ets>.]</ety> <def>The highest or utmost degree; the best of
anything.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tiptop</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Tiptop
<hw>Tip"top`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Very excellent; most excellent;
perfect.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Four <xex>tiptop</xex>
voices.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Gray.</au> ⟦ldquo⟧Sung in a <xex>tiptop</xex>
manner.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Goldsmith.</au>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tipula</ent>⟦br⟧
